    Used to describe an action used within an resource path For example: http://.../serviceroot/action()

    UriResourceCount
    Used to describe an $count used within an resource path For example: http://.../serviceroot/entityset(1)/$count

Package org.apache.olingo.server.api.uri Description

Olingo URI

The URI package is used to condense all information about the OData path used to query the data.
In order to support filter and orderby statements the ExpressionVisitor has to be implemented by an application.
